PROBLEM STATEMENT:
Reverse bits of a given 32 bits signed integer.

SOLUTION:

                                                                                    TIME COMPLEXITY: O(1)
                                                                                    SPACE COMPLEXITY: O(1)
class Solution {
    public int reverseBits(int n) {
        int res=0;
        for(int i=0; i<32; i++){
            res= res<<1;
            res|= (n&1);
            n= n>>1;
        }
        return res;
    }
}
